President Donald J. Trump has announced his intent to nominate several individuals to key positions in his administration. Robert Daigle of Virginia will serve as Director of Cost Assessment and Program Evaluation (CAPE) at the Department of Defense. Elaine McCusker of Virginia will serve as Principal Deputy Under Secretary of Defense, Comptroller. David L. Norquist of Virginia will serve as Under Secretary of Defense, Comptroller. Kenneth P. Rapuano of Virginia will serve as an Assistant Secretary of Defense, Homeland Defense and Global Security. Patrick M. Shanahan of Washington will serve as Deputy Secretary of Defense. David Joel Trachtenberg of Virginia will serve as Principal Deputy Under Secretary of Defense, Policy.